  "rationale": "Copy-first customer-evidence page in HubSpot's serif-display/sans-body register. The hero uses the hero-case-lead archetype (split-right per the SaaS directive): a right-hand heading column carrying the licensed orange-period landmark mark, balanced by a real Angel City FC case card (046-angel-fc.png) as the painted counterweight holding the 300%+ pulled stat, outcome line, and the quiet 'Read the story' action so the band keeps one action register (AS-59). Story renders the three atomic records as ONE feature-item array (3-up cards). Results carries the two facts as a single stat array on a cream panel to break surface cadence. Testimonial is a verbatim attributed quote on the page canvas. Pricing is intentionally novel (absent from the measured library) as one atomic card array with three complete records and per-record action variants, no table and no knobs. Closing reuses closing-cta-dark: a deep-teal inverse band (dark reserved for the closing sequence only) with a serif heading closed by the licensed period and the filled+outline action pair carried as one array. All headings stay sentence case at weight 500 or below; accent orange lives only in marks and controls."
